      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Massapequa_Park%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "The former Fitzmaurice Flying Field site now hosts McKenna Elementary School and the Nassau County Police Academy.",
